OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly cloudy and
OL,6,Fdry day with some bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells breaking through. A few
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain possible in the west
OL,9,Fwhere it will also be breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and largely cloudy
OL,12,Fnight for most with some clear
OL,13,Fintervals. A few outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fpossible in the west, and at times
OL,15,Fnear the east coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA few outbreaks of rain
OL,18,Fpossible near the coast in the east,
OL,19,Fbut otherwise it will be a dry day and
OL,20,Fmostly cloudy with some bright or
OL,21,Fsunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
